short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Control an arduino from the browser.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is a demo for running the Johnny Five library in the browser. 
You can turn LEDs on and off or move servos. More functionality soon. 
Source code available here https://github.com/garrows/browserbot-demos
